			<node ID="ID_816302618" TEXT="An Information Technology (IT) Security Policy identifies the rules and procedures for all individuals accessing and using an organizations IT assets and resources. Effective IT Security Policy is a model of the organization&#8217;s culture in which rules and procedures are driven from its employees approach to their information and work." />
