			<node ID="ID_1160360246" TEXT="Here the company&#8217;s security is not jeopardized but the consumer&#8217;s privacy is violated. New contracts between businesses and federal agencies are also good examples of how IT issues cut through the different layers between privacy confidentiality and security." />
			</node>
