		<node ID="ID_920696714" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RSA_%28algorithm%29" TEXT="RSA (cryptosystem) - Wikipedia">
			<node ID="ID_934426294" TEXT="RSA (Rivest&#8211;Shamir&#8211;Adleman) is one of the first public-key cryptosystems and is widely used for secure data transmission. In such a cryptosystem the encryption key is public and it is different from the decryption key which is kept secret (private). In RSA this asymmetry is based on the practical difficulty of the factorization of the product of two large prime numbers the factoring " />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_448731802" LINK="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25699187/rsa-encryption-output-size" TEXT="RSA encryption output size - Stack Overflow">
