			<node ID="ID_1027881880" TEXT="Diffie-Hellman is a way of generating a shared secret between two people in such a way that the secret cant be seen by observing the communication. Thats an important distinction: Youre not sharing information during the key exchange youre creating a key together. This is particularly useful because you can use this technique to create an encryption key with someone and then start " />
