			<node ID="ID_1758592350" TEXT="Diffie-Hellman Key Exchange: The Diffie-Hellmann key exchange is a secure method for exchanging cryptographic keys. This method allows two parties which have no prior knowledge of each other to establish a shared secret key even over an insecure channel. The concept uses multiplicative group of integers modulo which without knowledge of the " />
