			<node ID="ID_211997285" TEXT="Introduction to Diffie Hellman Key Exchange Algorithm. The Diffie Hellman Key Exchange Algorithm is one of the first practical implementations of the public key exchange in the field of cryptography.The Diffie Hellman Key Exchange Algorithm is one of the ways that can generate a shared key and share secrete between two parties in a way that we can be sure that no one will be able to snoop in " />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1183129926" LINK="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NmM9HA2MQGI" TEXT="Secret Key Exchange (Diffie-Hellman) - Computerphile - YouTube">
