			<node ID="ID_1144320660" TEXT="Diffie-Hellman algorithm The Diffie-Hellman algorithm is being used to establish a shared secret that can be used for secret communications while exchanging data over a public network using the elliptic curve to generate points and get the secret key using the parameters." />
