			<node ID="ID_985892764" TEXT="The representation of text in the form of a single string of digits created using a formula called a one-way hash function. Encrypting a message digest with a private key creates a digital signature which is an electronic means of authentication." />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_662807139" LINK="https://www.veracode.com/blog/research/message-digests-aka-hashing-functions" TEXT="Message Digests aka Hashing Functions | Veracode">
			<node ID="ID_968175076" TEXT="A message digest algorithm or a hash function is a procedure that maps input data of an arbitrary length to an output of fixed length. Output is often known as hash values hash codes hash sums checksums message digest digital fingerprint or simply hashes." />
			</node>
