			<node ID="ID_1632911386" TEXT="The Java MessageDigest class represents a cryptographic hash function which can calculate a message digest from binary data. When you receive some encrypted data you cannot see from the data itself whether it was modified during transportation. A message digest can help alleviate that problem." />
