			<node ID="ID_164135931" TEXT="Message digests (Hashing)&#182; class cryptography.hazmat.primitives.hashes.Hash (algorithm backend) [source] &#182;. A cryptographic hash function takes an arbitrary block of data and calculates a fixed-size bit string (a digest) such that different data results (with a high probability) in different digests." />
