			<node ID="ID_284757040" TEXT="Secure Electronic Transaction: A secure electronic transaction (SET) is an open-source and cryptography-based protocol for secure payment processing via nonsecure networks. In June 2003 SET was published as RFC 3538. SET was replaced by more advanced systems such VISA&#8217;s 3-D Secure." />
			</node>
