		<node ID="ID_837770789" LINK="https://cybercrimelawyer.wordpress.com/category/breach-of-confidentiality-and-privacy/" TEXT="Breach of confidentiality and privacy | Cyber Crime ">
			<node ID="ID_715935624" TEXT="This entry was posted in Breach of confidentiality and privacy Section 72 of IT Act 2000: Breach of confidentiality and privacy. and tagged Breach of confidentiality and privacy under IT Act. Section 72 of IT Act 2000: Breach of confidentiality and privacy. on May 16 2013 by Cyber Crime Lawyer in Delhi.India." />
