			<node ID="ID_156658221" TEXT="AGREEMENT FOR COMPUTER FORENSIC SERVICES This Agreement For Computer Forensic Services (this &#8220;Agreement&#8221;) is entered into as of _____ 2008 by and between name of company (&#8220;Consultant&#8221;) with a place of business at company address and _____(the &#8220;Client&#8221;). Consultant and the Client are collectively" />
